To exclude unnecessary files from your repository.

```plaintext
# Logs and temporary files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
.DS_Store

# history
.history/
# Docker-related
*.env
docker-compose.override.yml

# Python-related
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/

# Node.js (if ever used)
node_modules/

# Secrets
secrets.json